{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Boolean","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Boolean","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>コンピューター科学において、<strong>boolean</strong>（論理型、真偽値型）は <code>true</code>（真）か <code>false</code>（偽）の値のみを取れる論理データ型です。たとえば、 JavaScript では boolean による条件がコードの部分を実行するか（<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/if...else\">if 文</a>の中など）や繰り返し（<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/for\">for ループ</a>など）を決定します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* JavaScript if 文 */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>boolean 条件<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token comment\">// 条件が true の場合に実行するコード</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>boolean 条件<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"boolean 条件が true になった\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"boolean 条件が false になった\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* JavaScript for ループ */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>制御変数<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> boolean 条件<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> カウンター<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 条件が true の場合に繰り返し実行されるコード</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"boolean 条件が true の場合のみ表示\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基礎知識","title":"基礎知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>ウィキペディアの「<a title=\"ブーリアン型\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ブーリアン型\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ブーリアン型</a>」の記事</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術リファレンス","title":"技術リファレンス","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>JavaScript のグローバルオブジェクト: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Data_structures\">JavaScript のデータ構造</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"コンピューター科学において、boolean（論理型、真偽値型）は true（真）か false（偽）の値のみを取れる論理データ型です。たとえば、 JavaScript では boolean による条件がコードの部分を実行するか（if 文の中など）や繰り返し（for ループなど）を決定します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Boolean","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Boolean","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Booléen","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"불린","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Booleano","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Boolean (Булев, Логический тип данных)","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Boolean","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"布林","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/boolean","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/boolean/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Boolean","title":"Boolean"}],"pageTitle":"Boolean - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}